  "ai_usage": "Use for CLIs, SDKs, APIs, and infra/devtool products. The hero is a styled terminal window; a tiny typewriter loop types the LINES array (full text is also in the DOM for a11y). The install bar copies to clipboard. Recolor via --accent/--green. Replace LINES, the install command, features, and the code sample. Reduced-motion shows commands instantly.",
  "path": "effects/website-templates/terminal-devtool.html",
  "source": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n<title>Terminal — Developer Tool</title>\n<script type=\"application/json\" id=\"effect-meta\">\n{\n  \"id\": \"terminal-devtool\",\n  \"title\": \"Terminal — Developer Tool\",\n  \"summary\": \"A dark, code-forward landing for a CLI/dev tool: a faux terminal with a typing animation, monospace UI, an install command, and a code sample.\",\n  \"description\": \"The developer-tool aesthetic — monospace, dark, terminal-first. This landing opens with a working-looking terminal window that types its commands out, a one-line install with a copy button, a feature grid in code-comment style, and a syntax-tinted snippet. Built for CLIs, APIs, and infra products.\",\n  \"theme\": \"website-templates\",\n  \"categories\": [\"template\", \"landing\", \"developer\"],\n  \"tags\": [\"terminal\", \"developer-tool\", \"cli\", \"dark\", \"monospace\", \"code\", \"full-page\"],\n  \"tech\": [\"html\", \"css\", \"js\"],\n  \"era\": \"2020s\",\n  \"difficulty\": \"intermediate\",\n  \"dependencies\": [],\n  \"browser_support\": \"All modern browsers.\",\n  \"performance_notes\": \"A small typewriter loop (setTimeout) + copy-to-clipboard + reveals. No images or libraries.\",\n  \"accessibility_notes\": \"Terminal text is real text; the typing is decorative and the full command is present for screen readers. Copy button has a label and live status. Reduced-motion shows the command instantly.\",\n  \"customization\": [\n    { \"name\": \"--accent / --green\", \"description\": \"Prompt + highlight colors\", \"default\": \"violet / green\" },\n    { \"name\": \"typed lines\", \"description\": \"Array in the script\", \"default\": \"3 commands\" }\n  ],\n  \"variations\": [\"Light terminal (Solarized)\", \"Replace typing with a static log\", \"Swap snippet language\"],\n  \"related\": [\"typewriter-text\"],\n  \"ai_usage\": \"Use for CLIs, SDKs, APIs, and infra/devtool products. The hero is a styled terminal window; a tiny typewriter loop types the LINES array (full text is also in the DOM for a11y). The install bar copies to clipboard. Recolor via --accent/--green. Replace LINES, the install command, features, and the code sample. Reduced-motion shows commands instantly.\"\n}\n</script>\n<style>\n  :root{--bg:#0a0c10;--panel:#0f1216;--text:#d7dde6;--muted:#7b8694;--line:#1c2530;--accent:#a78bff;--green:#46e0a0;--blue:#5cb8ff;--orange:#ffb454;--r:12px;\n    --mono:ui-monospace,\"JetBrains Mono\",\"SF Mono\",Menlo,Consolas,monospace;}\n  *{box-sizing:border-box}html{scroll-behavior:smooth}\n  body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--mono);line-height:1.6;\n    background-image:radial-gradient(40vw 30vw at 80% -5%,rgba(167,139,255,.18),transparent 60%);}\n  a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}\n  .wrap{max-width:1040px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.4rem}\n  nav{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:64px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}\n  .brand{font-weight:700}.brand .p{color:var(--accent)}\n  .links{display:flex;gap:1.3rem;align-items:center;color:var(--muted);font-size:.9rem}.links a:hover{color:var(--text)}\n  .btn{display:inline-block;background:var(--accent);color:#0a0c10;font-weight:700;border:none;border-radius:8px;padding:.5rem 1rem;cursor:pointer;font-family:var(--mono)}\n  .btn:hover{filter:brightness(1.1)}.btn:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--green);outline-offset:2px}\n  .hero{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:2.4rem;align-items:center;padding:4.5rem 0 3.5rem}\n  .tagver{color:var(--green);font-size:.85rem}\n  h1{font-family:system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(2.2rem,4.6vw,3.4rem);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.1;margin:.8rem 0}\n  h1 .g{color:var(--accent)}\n  .sub{color:var(--muted);font-size:1.05rem;max-width:44ch;margin:0 0 1.4rem;font-family:system-ui,sans-serif}\n  .install{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.6rem;background:#0c1014;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:10px;padding:.7rem .9rem;max-width:380px}\n  .install code{color:var(--green)}.install code .d{color:var(--muted)}\n  .install button{margin-left:auto;background:none;border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--muted);border-radius:6px;padding:.25rem .6rem;cursor:pointer;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.8rem}\n  .install button:hover{color:var(--text);border-color:var(--accent)}\n  .term{background:#0c1014;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--r);overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.6)}\n  .term .bar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;padding:.6rem .9rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);background:#0a0d11}\n  .term .bar i{width:11px;height:11px;border-radius:50%}.r1{background:#ff5f57}.r2{background:#febc2e}.r3{background:#28c840}\n  .term .bar .t{margin-left:.6rem;color:var(--muted);font-size:.8rem}\n  .term .body{padding:1.1rem;min-height:210px;font-size:.92rem}\n  .term .line{white-space:pre-wrap}.term .pr{color:var(--accent)}.term .ok{color:var(--green)}.term .dim{color:var(--muted)}\n  .cursor{display:inline-block;width:8px;height:1.1em;background:var(--green);vertical-align:-2px;animation:blink 1s step-end infinite}\n  @keyframes blink{50%{opacity:0}}\n  section{padding:4rem 0}\n  .lbl{color:var(--muted);font-size:.85rem}.lbl .c{color:var(--accent)}\n  h2{font-family:system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(1.7rem,3.4vw,2.3rem);font-weight:800;margin:.3rem 0 2rem;letter-spacing:-.02em}\n  .feats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1rem}\n  .feat{background:#0d1116;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--r);padding:1.3rem}\n  .feat .c{color:var(--green);font-size:.82rem}.feat h3{font-family:system-ui,sans-serif;margin:.4rem 0 .3rem;font-size:1.08rem}.feat p{color:var(--muted);margin:0;font-size:.9rem;font-family:system-ui,sans-serif}\n  .snippet{background:#0c1014;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--r);padding:1.2rem;overflow:auto;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7}\n  .snippet .kw{color:var(--accent)}.snippet .fn{color:var(--blue)}.snippet .st{color:var(--green)}.snippet .cm{color:var(--muted)}.snippet .nm{color:var(--orange)}\n  footer{border-top:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--muted);text-align:center;padding:2.2rem 0;font-size:.85rem}\n  .reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);transition:opacity .6s,transform .6s ease}.reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:none}\n  @media(max-width:840px){.hero{grid-template-columns:1fr}.feats{grid-template-columns:1fr}.links a:not(.btn){display:none}}\n  @media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.cursor{animation:none}.reveal{opacity:1;transform:none;transition:none}html{scroll-behavior:auto}}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"wrap\">\n    <nav>\n      <div class=\"brand\"><span class=\"p\">~/</span>flux</div>\n      <div class=\"links\"><a href=\"#\">Docs</a><a href=\"#\">Pricing</a><a href=\"#\">Changelog</a><a href=\"#\">GitHub ↗</a><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\">Sign in</a></div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n      <div>\n        <span class=\"tagver\">v3.2 just shipped →</span>\n        <h1>Deploy in <span class=\"g\">one command</span>.</h1>\n        <p class=\"sub\">Flux is the build-and-ship CLI for modern teams. Zero config, instant rollbacks, edge by default.</p>\n        <div class=\"install\">\n          <code><span class=\"d\">$</span> npm i -g @flux/cli</code>\n          <button id=\"copy\" aria-label=\"Copy install command\">copy</button>\n        </div>\n        <p id=\"copied\" role=\"status\" class=\"dim\" style=\"min-height:1.1em;font-size:.8rem;margin:.5rem 0 0\"></p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"term\" aria-label=\"Terminal demo\">\n        <div class=\"bar\"><i class=\"r1\"></i><i class=\"r2\"></i><i class=\"r3\"></i><span class=\"t\">flux — deploy</span></div>\n        <div class=\"body\" id=\"term\"></div>\n      </div>\n    </header>\n  </div>\n\n  <section class=\"wrap\">\n    <div class=\"lbl\"><span class=\"c\">//</span> why flux</div>\n    <h2>Built for shipping fast</h2>\n    <div class=\"feats\">\n      <div class=\"feat reveal\"><div class=\"c\">// speed</div><h3>Sub-second builds</h3><p>Incremental, cached, and parallel out of the box.</p></div>\n      <div class=\"feat reveal\"><div class=\"c\">// safety</div><h3>Instant rollback</h3><p>Every deploy is atomic and reversible in one command.</p></div>\n      <div class=\"feat reveal\"><div class=\"c\">// reach</div><h3>Global edge</h3><p>300+ locations. Your app, close to everyone.</p></div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"wrap\">\n    <div class=\"lbl\"><span class=\"c\">//</span> config-as-code</div>\n    <h2>Readable by humans</h2>\n    <pre class=\"snippet reveal\"><code><span class=\"cm\"># flux.config.ts</span>\n<span class=\"kw\">import</span> { defineConfig } <span class=\"kw\">from</span> <span class=\"st\">'@flux/cli'</span>\n\n<span class=\"kw\">export default</span> <span class=\"fn\">defineConfig</span>({\n  app: <span class=\"st\">'storefront'</span>,\n  regions: [<span class=\"st\">'iad'</span>, <span class=\"st\">'fra'</span>, <span class=\"st\">'sin'</span>],\n  build: { command: <span class=\"st\">'pnpm build'</span>, output: <span class=\"st\">'dist'</span> },\n  rollback: <span class=\"nm\">true</span>,\n})</code></pre>\n  </section>\n\n  <footer class=\"wrap\">© <span id=\"yr\"></span> Flux · built by developers, for developers.</footer>\n\n  <script>\n    document.getElementById('yr').textContent=new Date().getFullYear();\n    // copy install\n    var copy=document.getElementById('copy'),copied=document.getElementById('copied');\n    copy.addEventListener('click',function(){\n      navigator.clipboard.writeText('npm i -g @flux/cli').then(function(){copied.textContent='✓ copied to clipboard';setTimeout(function(){copied.textContent=''},1800);});\n    });\n    // typewriter terminal\n    var term=document.getElementById('term');\n    var LINES=[\n      {t:'$ flux deploy',cls:'pr'},\n      {t:'→ building storefront…',cls:'dim'},\n      {t:'✓ build complete in 0.8s',cls:'ok'},\n      {t:'→ uploading to 312 edges…',cls:'dim'},\n      {t:'✓ live at https://storefront.flux.app',cls:'ok'},\n    ];\n    var reduce=matchMedia('(prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)').matches;\n    if(reduce){ term.innerHTML=LINES.map(function(l){return '<div class=\"line '+l.cls+'\">'+l.t+'</div>';}).join(''); }\n    else{\n      var li=0;\n      function typeLine(){\n        if(li>=LINES.length){ setTimeout(function(){term.innerHTML='';li=0;typeLine();},2600); return; }\n        var l=LINES[li], el=document.createElement('div'); el.className='line '+l.cls; term.appendChild(el);\n        var ci=0, cur=document.createElement('span'); cur.className='cursor'; el.appendChild(cur);\n        (function tick(){\n          if(ci<l.t.length){ cur.insertAdjacentText('beforebegin', l.t[ci++]); setTimeout(tick, 26); }\n          else { cur.remove(); li++; setTimeout(typeLine, 360); }\n        })();\n      }\n      typeLine();\n    }\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
}
